Phase 13 done.

- YouTube/local timeline slider seeks video and slides authoritatively from paused/cold/playing states.
- Player controls are QuickTime-style floating glass chrome, shown on activity/tap and auto-hidden.
- Center START overlay and folded layout switcher are implemented.
- Default layout is p2p/PiP (`overlap`) unless JSON overrides `layout.mode`.
- Homepage source nodes stream into the central player with scroll-intensified flow.
- Verified with `npm test` and `npm run smoke` (121/121).
